      "rationale": "NIH is the primary QoI and is directly linked to plasma-free hemoglobin through the power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger). The mechanistic chain from shear stress to red blood cell damage to hemoglobin release is documented in the V&V plan. QoI relevance meets required level."
